{"id":1,"parent_id":0,"book_id":0,"content_id":1,"language_id":0,"display_order":1,"title":"Friends by Mail","subtitle":"","short_title":"Friends by Mail","uri":"/friend/2013/04/friends-by-mail","content":[["div",{"id":"head1","uri":"/friend/2013/04/friends-by-mail.head1"},[".seriesTitle","Friends by Mail"]],[".resources",["div",{"id":"head1","uri":"/friend/2013/04/friends-by-mail/share-your-blessings.head1"},[".title","Share Your Blessings"],[".bio",["div",{"id":"p2","uri":"/friend/2013/04/friends-by-mail/share-your-blessings.p2"},"Donna M., age 11, Pangasinan, Philippines"]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"p3","uri":"/friend/2013/04/friends-by-mail/share-your-blessings.p3"},"My favorite story in the",["span.emphasis","Friend"],"is",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2012/03/the-coat.p1"},"“The Coat”"],"(March 2012), a true story from the childhood of President Heber J. Grant. The lesson I got is to share your blessings. When I saw that my classmate didn’t have food, I gave her some. Now she is my best friend."]],["div",{"id":"head1","uri":"/friend/2013/04/friends-by-mail/the-friend-is-fun.head1"},[".title","The",["span.emphasis","Friend"],"Is Fun!"],[".bio",["div",{"id":"p2","uri":"/friend/2013/04/friends-by-mail/the-friend-is-fun.p2"},"Tanner B., age 11, Minnesota, USA"]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"p3","uri":"/friend/2013/04/friends-by-mail/the-friend-is-fun.p3"},"I really enjoy reading the stories in the",["span.emphasis","Friend"],"each month. I like how they teach lessons in fun, short stories. It’s fun looking for the hidden CTR ring each month too!"]],["div",{"id":"head1","uri":"/friend/2013/04/friends-by-mail/a-friend-for-sisters.head1"},[".title","A",["span.emphasis","Friend"],"for Sisters"],[".bio",["div",{"id":"p2","uri":"/friend/2013/04/friends-by-mail/a-friend-for-sisters.p2"},"Mardi H., age 7, Utah, USA, with Whitni, age 3"]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"p3","uri":"/friend/2013/04/friends-by-mail/a-friend-for-sisters.p3"},"The happiest day of each month is when the",["span.emphasis","Friend"],"comes in the mail. I love to read all of the stories to my little sister."]],["div",{"id":"head1","uri":"/friend/2013/04/friends-by-mail/how-we-read-the-friend.head1"},[".title","How We Read the",["span.emphasis","Friend"]],[".bio",["div",{"id":"p2","uri":"/friend/2013/04/friends-by-mail/how-we-read-the-friend.p2"},"Amy and Adam I., ages 3 and 3, Utah, USA"]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"p3","uri":"/friend/2013/04/friends-by-mail/how-we-read-the-friend.p3"},"Amy and Adam are twins, and they like to look at the",["span.emphasis","Friend"],"together."]],["div",{"id":"head1","uri":"/friend/2013/04/friends-by-mail/dear-friends.head1"},[".title","Dear Friends,"]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"p2","uri":"/friend/2013/04/friends-by-mail/dear-friends.p2"},"There’s no more beautiful or sacred place on earth than a temple. It’s a place where Heavenly Father invites us to come inside to feel His Spirit and make special covenants that will help us return to Him."],["div",{"id":"p3","uri":"/friend/2013/04/friends-by-mail/dear-friends.p3"},"We hope this month’s",["span.emphasis","Friend"],"will help you learn more about the temple and look forward to the day when you can go inside!"],["div",{"id":"p4","uri":"/friend/2013/04/friends-by-mail/dear-friends.p4"},"Heavenly Father loves you!"],["div",{"id":"p5","uri":"/friend/2013/04/friends-by-mail/dear-friends.p5"},"The",["span.emphasis","Friend"]],["div",{"id":"p6","uri":"/friend/2013/04/friends-by-mail/dear-friends.p6"},"P.S. Write and tell us what",["span.emphasis","you"],"love about the temple."]],[".box-decor",{"id":"f1","uri":"/friend/2013/04/friends-by-mail.f1"},["div",{"id":"p2","uri":"/friend/2013/04/friends-by-mail.p2"},"Was there a letter or a story in this month’s issue that helped you? Tell us about it. Turn to",["a.crossRef",{"href":"/friend/2013/04/guide-to-the-friend.p1"},"page 48"],"to find out how."]]]],"refs":null}
